	* NGExtensions/NSString+misc.[hm]: improved, now works with any object
	  which supports KVC (v4.2.89)
	
2004-06-07  Helge Hess  <helge.hess@skyrix.com>

	* NGBundleManager.m: fixed gcc 3.4 warnings (v4.2.88)

